      UNION ALL SELECT 91 UNION ALL SELECT 92 UNION ALL SELECT 93 UNION ALL SELECT 94 UNION ALL SELECT 95 UNION ALL SELECT 96 UNION ALL SELECT 97 UNION ALL SELECT 98 UNION ALL SELECT 99 UNION ALL SELECT 100) nums;




/* ---------- C-2. Tibero (ID 2..100) ---------- */

SELECT LEVEL, 'M' || LPAD(LEVEL, 4, '0'), 'Kim DA ' || LEVEL, '900101-' || LPAD(LEVEL, 7, '0'), '010' || LPAD(LEVEL, 8, '0'), 'damo_payload_' || LPAD(LEVEL, 3, '0'), 'damo_auth_' || LPAD(LEVEL, 3, '0')
FROM dual CONNECT BY LEVEL <= 99;



COMMIT;
